<h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0;">Order Confirmed!</h2>
<p>Hi {{fullname}},</p>
<p>Thank you for your order! We've received it and are getting it ready for shipment. Your order number is <strong>#{{orderId}}</strong>.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase;">Order Summary</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        {{#each items}}
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; font-weight: 500;">{{productName}} x {{quantity}}</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right;">{{formatCurrency price}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px;">Total</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; color: #4f46e5;">{{formatCurrency total}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<p>We'll notify you as soon as your items are on their way!</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/account/orders/{{orderId}}" class="btn">View Order Details</a>
</div>
<div class="divider"></div>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">If you have any questions, reply to this email or visit our help center.</p>
